all_candidates.title: Lean4: How the theorem prover works and why it's the new competitive edge in AI
all_candidates.summary: Large language models (LLMs) have astounded the world with their capabilities, yet they remain plagued by unpredictability and hallucinations – confidently outputting incorrect information. In high-stakes domains like finance, medicine or autonomous systems, such unreliability is unacceptable. Enter Lean4 , an open-source programming language and interactive theorem prover becoming a key tool to inject rigor and certainty into AI systems.
